description: Kona Ice Memphis is rolling through the city, serving tropical shaved ice from the most unique entertainment vehicle you'll ever see. It is a one of a kind experience that serves a premium tropical shaved ice - the finest icy treat on the planet. This is NOT your typical lack-luster snow cone. The flavors are bold & delicious like nothing you've ever had! We served over 250,000 Kona's so come see what you are missing!
name: Kona Ice Memphis
